summary: AN ORDINANCE related to the Traffic Code, amending Sections 11.14.425, 11.16.120, 11.16.300, 11.23.120, 11.26.060, 11.26.080, 11.26.100, 11.26.220, 11.31.121, 11.72.220, 11.76.015, 11.76.020, 11.76.040, 11.76.050, and the titles of Chapter 11.76 and Section 11.76.010 of the Seattle Municipal Code, and adding a new Section 11.76.005 to provide regulations for payment for vehicular parking at pay stations.
